# Dashboard auth
# Dashboard sign-in uses API-backed email/password login.
# Seeded local users are created by `node apps/api/scripts/seed-demo.mjs`:
# ADMIN: admin@example.com / AdminPass123!
# EDITOR: editor@example.com / EditorPass123!
# REVIEWER: reviewer@example.com / ReviewerPass123!
# USER: normal_user@example.com / UserPass123!
